{"tid":1956610,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"入黎幫推NEODERM草菅人命 ,害死港島東中心工作既人,害死做美容既人,政府仲唔強制停美容中心,屌你","createTime":"2020-04-03T09:52:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T01:24:27.000Z","uid":38528,"like":33,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"c50b03b057f45d791675c302d9bbe2d158dc300b","tid":1956610,"uid":38528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:52:25.000Z","msg":"Neoderm旗下有幾間唔同既brand包括dermes、reenex、elyze、Evvus、Geneoo、VIGENE及haaz<br />\n而琴日有reenex既人中左武肺,所以琴日就決定關門<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/pg/reenex.HongKong/posts/?ref=page_internal\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fpg%2Freenex.HongKong%2Fposts%2F%3Fref%3Dpage_internal&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=44ba6c7c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/pg/reenex.HongKong/posts/?ref=page_internal</a><br />\n<br />\n點解我會話佢累撚死人? 因為依間閪野有一個culture,就係每星期一會上港島東中心67樓開摔數大會,而咁岩中招果條員工有份上去<br />\n而負責NEODERM個<span style=\"color: red;\">director上海大陸閪婆</span>,係neoderm第2把膠椅咁上下,就日日摔數,開少一日工都唔撚得,d員工就病到死下死下都要死頂上去比佢地摔,仲成日吹個cell armor防到武肺,食左連mask都唔撚洗用<br />\n<br />\n大家可以睇下<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157314331392252&amp;set=gm.2876701632405732&amp;type=3&amp;theater&amp;ifg=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fphoto.php%3Ffbid%3D10157314331392252%26set%3Dgm.2876701632405732%26type%3D3%26theater%26ifg%3D1&d=HDFqBNw8TQCe%2BIc9lyi2BvrL6OgrijQqmkkA1x3Ej7w%3D&h=a862354d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=10157314331392252&amp;set=gm.2876701632405732&amp;type=3&amp;theater&amp;ifg=1</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZBiDTWc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZBiDTWc.png&h=2b0c1801&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n原來兩條仆街喺病發之前就已經唔舒服作病，25號仲上咗港島東中心67樓開會，嗰時佢個樣已經病到死死吓 ,照咁睇黎,成棟港島東中心唔撚洗要,大家知道果到一日幾撚多人出出入入<br />\n而係29號先睇醫生,上左做確診個案<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ALm90E6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FALm90E6.png&h=892c04e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n依家間閪野仲比人踢爆下星期一復工,仲想害人,平日做facial 個價markup咁高都冇人理,平日個閪大陸上海婆點屌d員工都死忍,但今次終於有人出黎踢爆間野特登扮無事,仲想害人<br />\n<br />\n依家大約估到個途徑就係,25號發病上67樓開會,開足3粒鐘&gt;全間房既人中招&gt;全67樓既人大部份中招&gt;係港島東上上落落&gt;傳比唔同樓層既人&gt;傳比唔同公司&gt;中左招既員工落返鋪&gt;傳返比d客同其他美容師,好撚大獲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n條仆街政府咁都唔撚命令美容中心強制關14日,大爆發真係多得佢唔少<br />\nPS: 個員工有mask都照比個客傳染,所以有mask都好,對得耐一樣會出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c241a07d5d64871cca1e35c1841e7fac4e0cb7c2","tid":1956610,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:56:03.000Z","msg":"今次仆得街<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32db501efdfa6a92cebb803284d7d3afa5c64e5c","tid":1956610,"uid":17723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:57:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aaa9f151ba1c84180e412b5776277e36d7bbe0cb","tid":1956610,"uid":51621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:58:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a6c98164e42dab14439c6655dc35750c9f0f2dae","tid":1956610,"uid":52090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:59:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1397ced734e9b891a0092985f0dc315babbf9945","tid":1956610,"uid":288312,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T09:59:32.000Z","msg":"【抗疫兼抗暴政】行動post: 不如恢復十點和你嗌？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1956598\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1956598</a>"},{"pid":"b7d1e61c30046e7e10c23dd10e81644a7cdac24d","tid":1956610,"uid":129169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-03T10:0